oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Judges of the Tennessee Court of Criminal Appeals
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white group portrait of the judges of the Tennessee Court of Criminal Appeals seated in the courtroom of the Tennessee Supreme Court. From left: Judge Robert K. Dwyer, Judge Oris Hyder, Judge W. Wayne Oliver, Presiding Judge Mark A. Walker, Judge Charles Galbreath, Judge John A. Mitchell, and Judge William J. Russell.
